    function getCurrentWord(document, offset) {
        var i = offset - 1;
        var text = document.getText();
        while (i >= 0 && ' \t\n\r":{[()]},'.indexOf(text.charAt(i)) === -1) {
            i--;
        }
        return text.substring(i + 1, offset);
    }
